
# Django ecommerce project

## Setup

1. python -m venv venv
2. source venv/bin/activate
3. python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip
4. django-admin startproject ecommerce
5. cd ecommerce

## Paypal

PayPal links:

Create a PayPal account

Create a Sandbox account[https://developer.paypal.com/home/] <- You must first have a PayPal account to login to create your Sandbox accounts.

Login to your Sandbox accounts[https://www.sandbox.paypal.com/myaccount/summary]

PayPal API and documentation (Useful as a general reference ONLY)

Customize the PayPal buttons

Validate user input

